name: Lady of the Night
description:
Halloween series composed of three artworks, "Lady of the Night", "Voices from Beyond" and "Cry of Silence".

Lady of the Night

"In the twilight the candles were lit
In the twilight the creatures smiled
In the twilight the Lady awoke

The magic of existence was present
The voices and the cries through her echoed
Spirit of the black eyes
At her touch the darkness came alive
Until the dawn's awakening everything belonged to her".
